                        <p id="fs-idp1279024">
                          If we know the mass of a substance and its specific heat, we can determine the amount of heat,
                          <em data-effect="italics">q</em>, entering or leaving the substance by measuring the temperature change before and after the heat is gained or lost:
                        </p>
                        <div data-type="equation" id="fs-idp8176432">
                          <math display="block">
                            <semantics>
