                            Because the temperature increased, the water absorbed heat and
                            <em data-effect="italics">q</em> is positive.
                          </p>
                          <p id="fs-idm1147904">
                            <span data-type="title">Check Your Learning</span>How much heat, in joules, must be added to a 5.07
